| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4589 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6cc183e4-c2ee-5f08-80fc-2ed5750fc01a"
